cat << EOF
The KDE Bluetooth Framework is a set of tools built on top of Linux's Bluetooth
stack BlueZ. Our goal is to provide easy access to the most common Bluetooth
profiles and to make data exchange with Bluetooth enabled phones and PDAs as
straightforward as possible.
EOF
